      • compare

        public java.util.List<FCResult> compare(byte[] feature,
                                        int maxResult)
        1vN compare
        参数:
        feature - the feature to be compared
        maxResult - the max record to be returned, if the number of records less than the value specified, then return the records as it is.
        返回:
        the results that hit the threshold specified.list size is <= maxResult. The maxResult default is 5.
